{"tid":150473,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"其實 m 記 d $23 餐賣咁平有冇錢賺嫁？","createTime":"2017-03-10T05:32:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T04:58:28.000Z","uid":35400,"like":3,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7e594d0b50427da236e1f8fad4477395508d0754","tid":150473,"uid":35400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T05:32:21.000Z","msg":"用麥樂雞做例子<br />\n以下全部用成本價計<br />\n<br />\n1. 麥樂雞當佢成本 $2 一件 <br />\n6 件加埋都 $12<br />\n<br />\n2. 可樂 出面賣都要 $5 罐<br />\n我當佢入貨價 $4 好未 ???<br />\n<br />\n3. 薯條 呢個比較難預 因為佢一大包咁入貨<br />\n我當佢成本 $5 包 (中薯條咋，加大另計)<br />\n<br />\n4. 仲有茄汁呀 麥樂雞醬呀 <br />\n有時預到 d 比較小家既人又要比多幾包茄汁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢到預 $3<br />\n<br />\nTotal Cost = $12 + $4 + $5 + $3<br />\n= $24 &gt; $23<br />\n<br />\n仲未計埋 d 燈油火蠟 咁賣法 m 記咪蝕住黎做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以咁多年黎係咁加價都唔係冇道理喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6d962f99ccabbf295c3ae525c5ee37ad93e9c7e","tid":150473,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T05:35:38.000Z","msg":"樓主假膠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ca679132d5b4999cf46a39ce7a29fe60d66a253","tid":150473,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T05:35:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5fbfbdf5548467ef7ff2961087d87ed74804ef79","tid":150473,"uid":44748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T05:35:49.000Z","msg":"依家賣24wo"},{"pid":"4a203cc973659c3d7ae5b29b92a7b40782fa03fd","tid":150473,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T05:36:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用麥樂雞做例子<br />\n以下全部用成本價計<br />\n<br />\n1. 麥樂雞當佢成本 $2 一件 <br />\n6 件加埋都 $12<br />\n<br />\n2. 可樂 出面賣都要 $5 罐<br />\n我當佢入貨價 $4 好未 ???<br />\n<br />\n3. 薯條 呢個比較難預 因為佢一大包咁入貨<br />\n我當佢成本 $5 包 (中薯條咋，加大另計)<br />\n<br />\n4. 仲有茄汁呀 麥樂雞醬呀 <br />\n有時預到 d 比較小家既人又要比多幾包茄汁 <img sr